<% if @age < 75  %>
<h1>45 - 49 Year Old Health Assessments</h1>
<% else %>
<h1>75 + Year Old Health Assessments</h1>
<% end %>

There are <%= @totalCount %> patients in the age range. <%= @no_ass_patients.count %> ( <%= number_to_percentage(@no_ass_patients.count * 100 / @totalCount, precision: 0) %> ) have not had a health assessment performed <%= "in the last 12 months" if @age == 75 %>.<br>
<%= @mobileCount %> of these have a mobile phone number, and <%= @emailCount %> have an email address<p>
<% if @age == 50 %>
<%= @F49Count %> have already turned 49!<br>
<% end %>


<table class='table table-striped'>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Name</th>
<th>Age</th>
<th>Mobile</th>
<th>Last Seen</th>
<th>By</th>

</thead>
<tbody>
<% @no_ass_patients.each do |patient| %>
<tr>
	<td><%= patient["FULLNAME"]%></td>
	<td><%= age(patient["DOB"]) %></td>
	<td><%= patient["MOBILEPHONE"]%></td>
	<td><%= patient["LASTSEENDATE"].to_date.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") if patient["LASTSEENDATE"]%></td>
	<td><%= patient["LASTSEENBY"] %></td>

</tr>
<% end %>
</tbody>
</table>



<h2>Completed</h2>

These are the people who have had a health assessment.
<table class='table table-striped'>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Name</th>
<th>Age</th>
<th>Date</th>
<th>Done By</th>

</thead>
<tbody>
<% @ass_patients.each do |patient| %>
<tr>
	<td><%= patient["FULLNAME"]%></td>
	<td><%= age(patient["DOB"]) %></td>
	<td><%= patient[:SERVICEDATE].to_date.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %>
	<td><%= patient[:PROVIDERID] %></td>

</tr>
<% end %>
</tbody>
</table>
